## Installation & Setup

```bash
# Install dependencies
npm install

# Run in development
npm run dev

---

## API Overview

### Auth Routes

* `POST /api/auth/register`
* `POST /api/auth/login`
* `GET /api/auth/verify-email`

### Company Routes

* `POST /api/vacancies` – create vacancy
* `GET /api/vacancies/company` – view own vacancies
* `GET /api/vacancies/:id/applicants` – view applicants

### Applicant Routes

* `GET /api/vacancies` – view vacancies
* `POST /api/vacancies/:id/apply` – apply for vacancy

---

## Key Learning Outcomes

* Role-based access control (RBAC)
* Event-driven architecture using EventEmitter
* Secure file uploads with Multer
* Clean Express + TypeScript architecture
* Scalable backend folder structure

